    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 1080 361"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        style="width:100%; display:block; height: clamp(140px, 35vw, 280px);"
    >
        <path
            d="
      M 0,33 10,31 20,30 30,27 40,24 50,22 60,19 70,15 80,13 90,10 100,9 110,8 120,8 130,9 140,10 150,12 160,14 170,17 180,20 190,23 200,26 210,28 220,30 230,32 240,33 250,34 260,34 270,34 280,32 290,31 300,28 310,26 320,23 330,19 340,16 350,13 360,11 370,9 380,8 390,8 400,7 410,8 420,8 430,10 440,11 450,13 460,16 470,19 480,23 490,26 500,28 510,30 520,32 530,33 540,34 550,34 560,34 570,33 580,31 590,30 600,27 610,24 620,21 630,18 640,15 650,13 660,11 670,10 680,10 690,9 700,10 710,10 720,11 730,13 740,15 750,17 760,21 770,23 780,26 790,28 800,30 810,30 820,31 830,31 840,31 850,30 860,28 870,27 880,24 890,22 900,19 910,17 920,14 930,11 940,10 950,8 960,8 970,7 980,7 990,8 1000,8 1010,10 1020,11 1030,13 1040,15 1050,18 1060,21 1070,24 1079,28
      L 1079,349 1070,346 1060,342 1050,339 1040,337 1030,334 1020,332 1010,331 1000,330 990,329 980,329 970,329 960,329 950,330 940,331 930,333 920,335 910,338 900,341 890,344 880,346 870,349 860,350 850,352 840,352 830,353 820,352 810,352 800,351 790,349 780,346 770,344 760,341 750,337 740,335 730,332 720,331 710,330 700,329 690,329 680,329 670,330 660,331 650,332 640,335 630,337 620,341 610,343 600,346 590,348 580,350 570,352 560,352 550,353 540,353 530,352 520,351 510,350 500,348 490,345 480,342 470,339 460,337 450,334 440,332 430,331 420,330 410,330 400,330 390,331 380,331 370,333 360,335 350,337 340,341 330,343 320,346 310,348 300,350 290,352 280,352 270,353 260,353 250,352 240,351 230,350 220,348 210,346 200,343 190,341 180,337 170,335 160,333 150,331 140,330 130,329 120,129 110,128 100,129 90,330 80,330 70,331 60,333 50,335 40,337 30,340 20,343 10,346 0,349
      Z"
            fill="#ebccc4"></path>
        <foreignObject x="80" y="50" width="920" height="260">
            <div
                style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; height:100%; text-align:center;"
            >
                <p
                    class="font-callingstone text-[#63778d] uppercase font-bold text-[30px] sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-[0.19em]"
                >
                    Nuestra Historia
                </p>
            </div>
        </foreignObject>
    </svg>
</section>

<!-- CONTENIDO -->
<section class="py-6 px-4 relative overflow-hidden" id="seccion-galeria">
    <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto relative z-10">
        <!-- Línea decorativa -->
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6"
            id="linea-deco"
        >
            <div
                style="height:1px; width:60px; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ebccc4);"
            >
            </div>
            <span class="font-allura text-[#ebccc4]" style="font-size:1.4rem;"
                >♡</span
            >
            <div
                style="height:1px; width:60px; background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, #ebccc4);"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CARD TEXTO HISTORIA -->
        <div class="card-historia mb-10" id="card-historia">
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#63778d] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Caminamos por los mismos pasillos del colegio durante años sin
                saber que el destino nos tenía guardados para el momento justo.
                Una mirada en el lugar menos esperado fue el inicio de todo.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-[#ebccc4]/60"></div>
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#63778d] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Juntos descubrimos que la felicidad vive en los detalles, en las
                risas que no terminan y en esos abrazos que curan todo.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-[#ebccc4]/60"></div>
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#63778d] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Entendimos que el amor es el viaje más valioso y hemos decidido
                recorrerlo siempre de la mano.
            </p>
            <div class="relative w-full h-32 pointer-events-none mb-2">
                <img
                    src="/imagenes/florabajo.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="absolute bottom-10 -right-3 w-56 sm:w-44 object-contain z-20 scale-x-[-1]"
                    id="flor-galeria"
                />
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#ebccc4] leading-relaxed text-center font-bold tracking-widest"
            >
                Nuestra boda es una celebración del amor, pero también de la
                amistad.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CARRUSEL CINEMATOGRÁFICO -->
        <div id="galeria-wrapper" class="relative w-full">
            <!-- Frame decorativo -->
            <div
                class="frame-deco absolute -inset-3 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none z-0"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#ebccc4]/40 rounded-tl-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#ebccc4]/40 rounded-tr-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#ebccc4]/40 rounded-bl-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#ebccc4]/40 rounded-br-2xl"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Slides -->
            <div
                class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] z-10"
                id="slides-viewport"
                style="aspect-ratio: 3/4;"
            >
                <!-- generado por JS -->
            </div>

            <!-- Overlay degradado inferior -->
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 z-20 pointer-events-none rounded-b-[1.5rem]"
                style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.45), transparent);"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- Número flotante elegante -->
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-30 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-6 h-px bg-white/40"></div>
                <span
                    id="num-slide"
                    class="font-cathylise text-white/80 text-lg tracking-widest"
                    >01</span
                >
                <div class="w-6 h-px bg-white/40"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Barra de progreso circular -->
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-30">
                <svg
                    width="36"
                    height="36"
                    viewBox="0 0 36 36"
                    class="rotate-[-90deg]"
                >
                    <circle
                        cx="18"
                        cy="18"
                        r="15"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"
                        stroke-width="2"></circle>
                    <circle
                        id="progreso-circulo"
                        cx="18"
                        cy="18"
                        r="15"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="rgba(235,204,196,0.9)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-dasharray="94.2"
                        stroke-dashoffset="94.2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"></circle>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <!-- Puntos laterales -->
            <div
                class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-30 flex flex-col gap-2"
                id="dots-lateral"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Crédito elegante debajo -->
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-6"
            id="credito-galeria"
        >
            <div
                style="height:1px; flex:1; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #ebccc4);"
            >
            </div>
            <span
                class="font-callingstone text-[#ebccc4]/60 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase"
                >Nuestra historia</span
            >
            <div
                style="height:1px; flex:1; background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, #ebccc4);"
            >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MODAL FULLSCREEN -->
    <div
        id="modal-galeria"
        class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center"
        style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.96);"
    >
        <!-- Partículas decorativas -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden"
            id="modal-particulas"
        >
        </div>

        <button
            id="cerrar-modal"
            class="absolute top-6 right-6 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-500 z-50 hover:rotate-90"
            style="background: rgba(235,204,196,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.3);"
        >
            <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#ebccc4"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
            </svg>
        </button>

        <div
            class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 md:px-20"
        >
            <button
                id="btn-anterior"
                class="absolute left-3 md:left-8 z-40 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                style="background: rgba(235,204,196,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.25);"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#ebccc4"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>

            <div
                class="relative w-full max-w-xs md:max-w-md z-30"
                id="modal-contenido"
            >
                <!-- Marco decorativo modal -->
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 pointer-events-none">
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-l border-[#ebccc4]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-r border-[#ebccc4]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-l border-[#ebccc4]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-r border-[#ebccc4]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="modal-track" class="flex will-change-transform"></div>

                <!-- Info inferior modal -->
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex items-center gap-3 whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                    <span
                        id="modal-num"
                        class="font-cathylise text-[#ebccc4]/70 text-base"
                        >01</span
                    >
                    <div class="flex gap-1" id="modal-dots-mini"></div>
                    <span
                        class="font-cathylise text-white/30 text-base"
                        id="modal-total">03</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <button
                id="btn-siguiente"
                class="absolute right-3 md:right-8 z-40 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                style="background: rgba(235,204,196,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.25);"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#ebccc4"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";
    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            // ── ANIMACIONES ENTRADA ──
            gsap.set("#galeria-onda", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
            gsap.set("#card-historia", { opacity: 0, y: 30 });
            gsap.set("#flor-galeria", { opacity: 0, x: 30 });
            gsap.set("#galeria-wrapper", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.96 });
            gsap.set("#credito-galeria", { opacity: 0 });

            ScrollTrigger.create({
                trigger: "#seccion-galeria",
                start: "top 85%",
                onEnter: () => {
                    const tl = gsap.timeline();
                    tl.to("#galeria-onda", {
                        opacity: 1,
                        y: 0,
                        duration: 0.8,
                        ease: "power2.out",
                    })
                        .to(
                            "#flor-galeria",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                x: 0,
                                duration: 0.7,
                                ease: "power2.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.4",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#card-historia",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                y: 0,
                                duration: 0.8,
                                ease: "power2.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.4",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#galeria-wrapper",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                scale: 1,
                                duration: 1,
                                ease: "power3.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.3",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#credito-galeria",
                            { opacity: 1, duration: 0.6 },
                            "-=0.3",
                        );
                },
                onLeaveBack: () => {
                    gsap.set("#galeria-onda", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
                    gsap.set("#card-historia", { opacity: 0, y: 30 });
                    gsap.set("#flor-galeria", { opacity: 0, x: 30 });
                    gsap.set("#galeria-wrapper", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.96 });
                    gsap.set("#credito-galeria", { opacity: 0 });
                },
            });

            // ── FOTOS ──
            const fotos = [
                { src: "/imagenes/Foto1.webp", alt: "Nuestra historia 1" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto2.webp", alt: "Nuestra historia 2" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto3.webp", alt: "Nuestra historia 3" },
            ];

            const DURACION = 4500;
            const viewport = document.getElementById("slides-viewport");
            const dotsLateral = document.getElementById("dots-lateral");
            const numSlide = document.getElementById("num-slide");
            const progresoCirculo = document.getElementById("progreso-circulo");
            const CIRCUNFERENCIA = 94.2;

            // Crear slides con efecto Ken Burns
            fotos.forEach((foto, i) => {
                if (!viewport) return;
                const slide = document.createElement("div");
                slide.className = "slide-item absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer";
                slide.setAttribute("data-index", i.toString());
                slide.style.opacity = i === 0 ? "1" : "0";
                slide.style.zIndex = i === 0 ? "2" : "1";
                slide.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="w-full h-full overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="${foto.src}" alt="${foto.alt}"
                            class="slide-img w-full h-full object-cover"
                            style="transform-origin: center center;" />
                    </div>
                    <!-- Overlay elegante -->
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 transition-opacity duration-700"
                        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(235,204,196,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%, rgba(99,119,141,0.06) 100%);">
                    </div>
                    <!-- Icono al hover -->
                    <div class="slide-hover-icon absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
                                style="background: rgba(235,204,196,0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.4);">
                                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="#ebccc4" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <circle cx="10.5" cy="10.5" r="6.5" stroke-width="1.5"></circle>
                                    <path d="M15.5 15.5L21 21" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Anillo pulsante -->
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full animate-ping"
                                style="border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.3);"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                `;

                slide.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
                    const icon = slide.querySelector(
                        ".slide-hover-icon",
                    ) as HTMLElement;
                    if (icon) icon.style.opacity = "1";
                });
                slide.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
                    const icon = slide.querySelector(
                        ".slide-hover-icon",
                    ) as HTMLElement;
                    if (icon) icon.style.opacity = "0";
                });
                slide.addEventListener("click", () => abrirModal(i));
                viewport.appendChild(slide);

                // Dot lateral
                if (dotsLateral) {
                    const dot = document.createElement("div");
                    dot.className =
                        "dot-lat transition-all duration-500 rounded-full";
                    dot.style.cssText = `width: ${i === 0 ? "8px" : "4px"}; height: ${i === 0 ? "8px" : "4px"}; background: ${i === 0 ? "rgba(235,204,196,0.9)" : "rgba(235,204,196,0.3)"}`;
                    dotsLateral.appendChild(dot);
                }
            });

            // ── ANIMACIÓN KEN BURNS ──
            let kbTween: gsap.core.Tween | null = null;
            function iniciarKenBurns(index: number) {
                if (kbTween) kbTween.kill();
                const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide-item");
                const img = slides[index]?.querySelector(
                    ".slide-img",
                ) as HTMLElement;
                if (!img) return;
                gsap.set(img, { scale: 1, x: "0%", y: "0%" });
                const dirs = [
                    { scale: 1.08, x: "-2%", y: "-2%" },
                    { scale: 1.08, x: "2%", y: "-1%" },
                    { scale: 1.06, x: "-1%", y: "2%" },
                ];
                const d = dirs[index % dirs.length];
                kbTween = gsap.to(img, {
                    scale: d.scale,
                    x: d.x,
                    y: d.y,
                    duration: DURACION / 1000 + 1,
                    ease: "none",
                });
            }

            // ── PROGRESO CIRCULAR ──
            let progresoTween: gsap.core.Tween | null = null;
            function iniciarProgreso() {
                if (progresoTween) progresoTween.kill();
                if (!progresoCirculo) return;
                gsap.set(progresoCirculo, { strokeDashoffset: CIRCUNFERENCIA });
                progresoTween = gsap.to(progresoCirculo, {
                    strokeDashoffset: 0,
                    duration: DURACION / 1000,
                    ease: "none",
                });
            }

            // ── CAMBIO DE SLIDE con CROSSFADE ──
            let slideActual = 0;
            let autoTimer: ReturnType<typeof setTimeout>;
            let pausado = false;

            function actualizarDots(index: number) {
                const dots = document.querySelectorAll(".dot-lat");
                dots.forEach((d, i) => {
                    const el = d as HTMLElement;
                    el.style.width = i === index ? "8px" : "4px";
                    el.style.height = i === index ? "8px" : "4px";
                    el.style.background =
                        i === index
                            ? "rgba(235,204,196,0.9)"
                            : "rgba(235,204,196,0.3)";
                });
                if (numSlide)
                    numSlide.textContent = String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0");
            }

            function irASlide(nuevoIndex: number) {
                const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide-item");
                const anterior = slideActual;
                slideActual = (nuevoIndex + fotos.length) % fotos.length;

                // Crossfade elegante
                const slideAnterior = slides[anterior] as HTMLElement;
                const slideSiguiente = slides[slideActual] as HTMLElement;

                gsap.set(slideSiguiente, { opacity: 0, zIndex: 3 });
                gsap.set(slideAnterior, { zIndex: 2 });

                gsap.to(slideSiguiente, {
                    opacity: 1,
                    duration: 1.4,
                    ease: "power2.inOut",
                    onComplete: () => {
                        gsap.set(slideAnterior, { opacity: 0, zIndex: 1 });
                        gsap.set(slideSiguiente, { zIndex: 2 });
                    },
                });

                actualizarDots(slideActual);
                iniciarKenBurns(slideActual);
                iniciarProgreso();
            }

            function programarSiguiente() {
                clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                autoTimer = setTimeout(() => {
                    if (!pausado) {
                        irASlide(slideActual + 1);
                        programarSiguiente();
                    }
                }, DURACION);
            }

            // Hover pausa
            const wrapper = document.getElementById("galeria-wrapper");
            wrapper?.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
                pausado = true;
                progresoTween?.pause();
                kbTween?.pause();
            });
            wrapper?.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
                pausado = false;
                progresoTween?.resume();
                kbTween?.resume();
                programarSiguiente();
            });

            // Touch swipe
            let touchX = 0;
            viewport?.addEventListener(
                "touchstart",
                (e) => {
                    touchX = e.touches[0].clientX;
                },
                { passive: true },
            );
            viewport?.addEventListener("touchend", (e) => {
                const diff = touchX - e.changedTouches[0].clientX;
                if (Math.abs(diff) > 50) {
                    irASlide(diff > 0 ? slideActual + 1 : slideActual - 1);
                    programarSiguiente();
                }
            });

            // Iniciar
            iniciarKenBurns(0);
            iniciarProgreso();
            programarSiguiente();
            actualizarDots(0);

            // ── MODAL ──
            const modal = document.getElementById("modal-galeria");
            const modalTrack = document.getElementById("modal-track");
            const modalNum = document.getElementById("modal-num");
            const modalTotal = document.getElementById("modal-total");
            const modalDotsMini = document.getElementById("modal-dots-mini");
            const btnAnterior = document.getElementById("btn-anterior");
            const btnSiguiente = document.getElementById("btn-siguiente");
            const cerrarModalBtn = document.getElementById("cerrar-modal");

            if (modalTotal)
                modalTotal.textContent = String(fotos.length).padStart(2, "0");

            // Construir slides modal
            fotos.forEach((foto) => {
                if (!modalTrack) return;
                const slide = document.createElement("div");
                slide.className =
                    "min-w-full flex items-center justify-center px-2";
                slide.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="relative w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border: 1px solid rgba(235,204,196,0.15);">
                        <img src="${foto.src}" alt="${foto.alt}"
                            class="w-full h-auto max-h-[80vh] object-contain"
                            style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);" />
                    </div>
                `;
                modalTrack.appendChild(slide);
            });

            // Dots mini modal
            fotos.forEach((_, i) => {
                if (!modalDotsMini) return;
                const d = document.createElement("div");
                d.className =
                    "modal-dot-mini rounded-full transition-all duration-400";
                d.style.cssText = `width: ${i === 0 ? "16px" : "4px"}; height: 4px; background: ${i === 0 ? "rgba(235,204,196,0.8)" : "rgba(235,204,196,0.2)"}`;
                modalDotsMini.appendChild(d);
            });

            let indiceModal = 0;

            function actualizarModalDots(index: number) {
                document.querySelectorAll(".modal-dot-mini").forEach((d, i) => {
                    const el = d as HTMLElement;
                    el.style.width = i === index ? "16px" : "4px";
                    el.style.background =
                        i === index
                            ? "rgba(235,204,196,0.8)"
                            : "rgba(235,204,196,0.2)";
                });
                if (modalNum)
                    modalNum.textContent = String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0");
            }

            const moverModal = (nuevo: number, animar = true) => {
                if (!modalTrack) return;
                indiceModal = (nuevo + fotos.length) % fotos.length;
                if (animar) {
                    gsap.to(modalTrack, {
                        x: `-${indiceModal * 100}%`,
                        duration: 0.6,
                        ease: "power3.out",
                    });
                } else {
                    gsap.set(modalTrack, { x: `-${indiceModal * 100}%` });
                }
                actualizarModalDots(indiceModal);
            };

            // Partículas decorativas en modal
            function crearParticulas() {
                const container = document.getElementById("modal-particulas");
                if (!container) return;
                container.innerHTML = "";
                for (let i = 0; i < 12; i++) {
                    const p = document.createElement("div");
                    p.style.cssText = `
                        position: absolute;
                        width: ${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px;
                        height: ${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px;
                        background: rgba(235,204,196,${Math.random() * 0.3 + 0.1});
                        border-radius: 50%;
                        left: ${Math.random() * 100}%;
                        top: ${Math.random() * 100}%;
                    `;
                    container.appendChild(p);
                    gsap.to(p, {
                        y: -30 - Math.random() * 40,
                        x: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 20,
                        opacity: 0,
                        duration: 3 + Math.random() * 4,
                        repeat: -1,
                        delay: Math.random() * 3,
                        ease: "none",
                    });
                }
            }

            const abrirModal = (indice: number) => {
                if (!modal) return;
                pausado = true;
                clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                modal.classList.remove("hidden");
                modal.classList.add("flex");
                document.body.style.overflow = "hidden";
                moverModal(indice, false);
                crearParticulas();
                gsap.fromTo(
                    modal,
                    { opacity: 0 },
                    { opacity: 1, duration: 0.5, ease: "power2.out" },
                );
                gsap.fromTo(
                    "#modal-contenido",
                    { scale: 0.88, opacity: 0, y: 20 },
                    {
                        scale: 1,
                        opacity: 1,
                        y: 0,
                        duration: 0.7,
                        ease: "power3.out",
                        delay: 0.1,
                    },
                );
            };

            const cerrarModalFn = () => {
                if (!modal) return;
                gsap.to("#modal-contenido", {
                    scale: 0.88,
                    opacity: 0,
                    y: 20,
                    duration: 0.4,
                    ease: "power2.in",
                });
                gsap.to(modal, {
                    opacity: 0,
                    duration: 0.4,
                    ease: "power2.in",
                    delay: 0.15,
                    onComplete: () => {
                        modal.classList.add("hidden");
                        modal.classList.remove("flex");
                        document.body.style.overflow = "";
                        pausado = false;
                        iniciarProgreso();
                        programarSiguiente();
                    },
                });
            };

            btnAnterior?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                moverModal(indiceModal - 1);
            });
            btnSiguiente?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                moverModal(indiceModal + 1);
            });
            cerrarModalBtn?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                cerrarModalFn();
            });
            modal?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                if (e.target === modal) cerrarModalFn();
            });

            document.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
                if (modal && !modal.classList.contains("hidden")) {
                    if (e.key === "Escape") cerrarModalFn();
                    if (e.key === "ArrowLeft") moverModal(indiceModal - 1);
                    if (e.key === "ArrowRight") moverModal(indiceModal + 1);
                }
            });

            let mTouchX = 0;
            modal?.addEventListener(
                "touchstart",
                (e) => {
                    mTouchX = e.touches[0].clientX;
                },
                { passive: true },
            );
            modal?.addEventListener("touchend", (e) => {
                const diff = mTouchX - e.changedTouches[0].clientX;
                if (Math.abs(diff) > 60)
                    moverModal(diff > 0 ? indiceModal + 1 : indiceModal - 1);
            });
        });
    }
</script>

<style>
    .card-historia {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(235, 204, 196, 0.25);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 28px 24px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .card-historia:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(235, 204, 196, 0.12);
    }
    #slides-viewport {
        position: relative;
    }
    .slide-item {
        will-change: opacity;
    }
    .slide-img {
        will-change: transform;
    }
    #modal-track {
        will-change: transform;
        display: flex;
    }
    @keyframes ping {
        75%,
        100% {
            transform: scale(1.6);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-ping {
        animation: ping 1.5s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;
    }
</style>
